# Build context excludes for packaging/Containerfile (OpenShift + podman builds).
# The image does its own `npm ci` + `npm run build`, so host artifacts must not
# leak in: they would be wrong-arch, stale, or huge.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/coverage
**/playwright-report
**/test-results
**/.vite
.git
lab
docs
*.log
